COUNCIL DECISION&amp;#13;
on the position to be adopted on behalf of the European Union at the International&amp;#13;
Maritime Organization during the 70th and 71st session of the Marine Environment&amp;#13;
Protection Committee on the approval and adoption of amendments to MARPOL&amp;#13;
Annex VI concerning the designation and taking effect of the Baltic Sea and North Sea&amp;#13;
as Nitrogen Oxyde Emissions Control Area (NECA)</j.0:title>
